title: THE OLD MAN AND THE SEA - Hemingway. Frank Muller {FerraBit}
description:
THE OLD MAN AND THE SEA, by Earnest Hemingway (1952)

Narrated by Frank Muller
Unabridged, 3 CDs, 2.75 hours.

Recorded Books LLC, 1996. 
ISBN-10: 0788734121  ISBN-13: 978-0788734120
Appears to be out of print.

Converted my copy to MP3 (iTunes 8, 64kbps VBR).

The full cover, and a PDF copy, are included.

The book is a well known classic, and Frank Muller is (was)
"the first true superstar of spoken audio."

Cheers, FerraBit
January 2009
